      &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/11/07/B4hcFg.png&#34; alt=&#34;生命周期概述&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
